### Create a new notification
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": 1,
  "type": "order_status",
  "title": "Order Update",
  "message": "Your order has been shipped",
  "data": {
    "orderId": 123
  },
  "channel": "in_app"
}

### Get all notifications (optional unread filter)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/notifications?unread=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get unread notifications count
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/notifications/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get notification by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/notifications/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update a notification
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/notifications/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Order Update",
  "message": "Your order has been delivered",
  "is_read": true
}

### Mark a notification as read
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/notifications/1/read
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Mark all notifications as read
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/notifications/mark-all-read
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete a notification
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/notifications/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
